# NoBrainFog environment templates

NoBrainFog now supports running multiple adapters at the same time by starting one process per adapter with an explicit env file.

Use these adapter-specific examples instead:

- `discord.env.example` -> copy to `/root/nobrainfog-config/discord.env`
- `wechat.env.example` -> copy to `/root/nobrainfog-config/wechat.env`

Both real env files should point to the same shared data file:

```env
MD_PATH=/root/nbf-vault/todo.md
```

Start each adapter explicitly:

```bash
python main.py --env-file /root/nobrainfog-config/discord.env
python main.py --env-file /root/nobrainfog-config/wechat.env
```

Do not commit real env files. They may contain Discord tokens, WeChat Work secrets, and AI API keys.
